{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "wenrun-api-collection",
    "name": "温润 WenRun 门诊 API",
    "description": "## 使用说明\n\n1. **导入**：Postman → Import → 选择本文件。\n2. **环境**：集合变量 `baseUrl` 默认 `http://localhost:8080`，可按需修改。\n3. **登录**：先执行「认证 → 登录」；成功后会自动把 `token` 写入集合变量。\n4. **鉴权**：除「健康检查」「登录」外，其余接口需 Bearer Token（集合已配置 `{{token}}`）。也可使用请求头 `X-Token: {{token}}`。\n5. **演示账号**（`demo_data.sql`）：`admin` / `doctor01` / `cashier01` / `pharma01`，密码均为 `password`。\n\n## 统一响应\n\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": 200,\n  \"message\": \"success\",\n  \"data\": {}\n}\n```\n\n`code = 200` 表示成功；失败时 `data` 为 `null`。\n\n## AI 接口\n\n需先启动 Python FastAPI（默认 `http://127.0.0.1:8000`），Java 再转发至 `/v1/chat`。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "patientId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "scheduleId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "registrationId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "visitId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "prescriptionId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "chargeId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "deptId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "staffId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "drugId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "itemId", "value": "1" },
    { "key": "conversationId", "value": "00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "系统",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "健康检查",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
            "description": "无需登录。返回服务是否存活。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "登录",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = res.data && (res.data.token || res.data.accessToken);",
                  "if (res.code === 200 && token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "    console.log('已保存 token');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.warn('登录失败，未写入 token');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
            "description": "演示账号：admin / doctor01 / cashier01 / pharma01，密码均为 password。成功后自动保存 token（兼容 accessToken）。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "注册",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "const token = res.data && (res.data.token || res.data.accessToken);",
                  "if (res.code === 200 && token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "    console.log('注册成功，已保存 token');",
                  "} else {",
                  "    console.warn('注册失败，未写入 token');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"patient_demo\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"confirmPassword\": \"password\",\n  \"phone\": \"13900001234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
            "description": "患者自助注册。密码不少于 6 位；confirmPassword 须与 password 一致。成功后自动保存 token，真实姓名可在「个人中心 → 更新个人资料」补充。"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "退出登录",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout",
            "description": "从 Header 读取 token 并使其失效。"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
